<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-CN-1616-J - 干，你不是说你没复习吗？<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3699277&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602417700" alt="BenjaminChong" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3699277)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;">BenjaminChong</a></span><br />
